                                                                      <h3 class="vs-portfolio-title"><span>Shipt -Grocery app</span>
                                                                      </h3>
                                                                  </div>
                                                              </div>
                                                              <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Shipt is a grocery delivery service that allows customers to order groceries and have them delivered to their doorstep. The app enables users to browse through a variety of products, select items for purchase, and choose a delivery time that is convenient for them.</p>

